OL,3,CSecurity failings found at HMP
OL,4,CWandsworth in wake of alleged prisoner
OL,5,Cescape
OL,7,FAn audit found a raft of security
OL,8,Ffailings at HMP Wandsworth, a category
OL,9,FB prison in London, where prisoner
OL,10,FDaniel Khalife allegedly escaped last
OL,11,FSeptember.
OL,13,FHMP Wandsworth's Independent
OL,14,FMonitoring Board (IMB) said a security
OL,15,Faudit identified "81 points of
OL,16,Ffailure" and resulted in "long
OL,17,Foverdue" upgrades being made to CCTV
OL,18,Fcameras which had not worked for over
OL,19,Fa year.
