OL,7,FThe audit resulted in the prison being
OL,8,Fhanded the lowest grade of
OL,9,Funsatisfactory.
OL,11,FDaniel Khalife has been accused of
OL,12,Ffleeing custody while being held on
OL,13,Fremand over spy charges.
OL,15,FHe allegedly strapped himself
OL,16,Funderneath a food delivery lorry and
OL,17,Fwas arrested a few days later. The
OL,18,Fformer soldier denies all the charges
OL,19,Fagainst him and is due to stand trial
OL,20,Fin October.
