OL,7,FThe prisons watchdog called for the
OL,8,Fcategory B Victorian jail in south-
OL,9,Fwest London to be put into emergency
OL,10,Fmeasures after "deeply concerning"
OL,11,Finspection findings in the wake of the
OL,12,Falleged incident.
OL,14,FChief inspector of prisons Charlie
OL,15,FTaylor wrote to then justice secretary
OL,16,FAlex Chalk in May to issue an urgent
OL,17,Fnotification for improvement.
