OL,7,FEarlier this month the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice (MoJ) announced it would be
OL,9,Fredirecting #100 million from across
OL,10,Fthe prison service to spend over five
OL,11,Fyears on bringing in "urgent
OL,12,Fimprovements".
OL,14,FThe MoJ said it would also send in
OL,15,Fextra specialist staff after the full
OL,16,Fdetails of Mr Taylor's inspection were
OL,17,Fpublished, laying bare a "shocking"
OL,18,Flevel of chaos at the prison with
OL,19,Fstaff unable to "account for prisoners
OL,20,Fduring the working day".
