OL,7,FThe security audit was carried out in
OL,8,FNovember while an internal review
OL,9,Fcompleted in December made 39
OL,10,Frecommendations, the report said.
OL,12,FThe MoJ is yet to publish these
OL,13,Fdocuments or confirm whether any
OL,14,Fdisciplinary action has been taken.
