OL,7,FWhile the IMB - made up of volunteers
OL,8,Ftasked by ministers to scrutinise
OL,9,Fconditions in custody - welcomed the
OL,10,Fimprovements in security at the gate
OL,11,Fand reception, it warned it was
OL,12,F"possible" the measures "led to an
OL,13,Fincrease in drone activity.
OL,15,FThere were 261 instances noted during
OL,16,Fthe reporting period, with such
OL,17,Factivity relatively rare in the
OL,18,Fprevious year.
