OL,7,FThe shortage of experienced staff,
OL,8,Fwith almost half having been in their
OL,9,Fjob for less than a year, "undermined
OL,10,Fattempts to make the prison run
OL,11,Feffectively" and staff absence often
OL,12,Freached 50%, it said.
OL,14,FIMB chairman Matthew Andrews said:
OL,15,F"For HMP Wandsworth and the men whose
OL,16,Ftreatment we monitor, this year has
OL,17,Fbeen as bad as any in our memory and,
OL,18,Fby many measures, worse."
