OL,7,FAn investigation by ITV News last
OL,8,FOctober revealed the filthy conditions
OL,9,Fat Wandsworth Prison, including rats,
OL,10,Fbroken toilets and a lack of hot food
OL,11,Fand water for inmates.
OL,13,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "The new government inherited a
OL,15,Fjustice system in crisis and has been
OL,16,Fforced to take action and get a grip
OL,17,Fof the situation across the prison
OL,18,Festate, so we can lock up dangerous
OL,19,Foffenders, protect the public and make
OL,20,Fprisons safer for hard-working staff.
